Some things to consider,

FI gas tank has return outlet, only one on carbs

Location for FI computer in sheet metal

FI high pressure pump required from donor

Fuel pressure regulator/decel valve/relays/resistor block from doror
bus firewall

Vanagon engine has dipstick fitting problem in baywindow if I recall

